  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676130/extras/b16c602969b613c62dbe6d88d7255257.avif?t=1737936895\" width=660 height=198 /></span><br><br>Singaporeans have reported ghost sightings of Kiki, a calligrapher who had passed away several years ago. Meanwhile, Vinty receives a mysterious mail with a plane ticket to Singapore. As an aspiring calligrapher, she must learn the truth behind those Kiki appearances.<br><br>Even in death, Kiki continues to steal the spotlight. Must Vinty remain as a nobody for as long as she lives (yeah, probably)?<br><br><i>\"Make sure you stay hydrated honey!\" </i>- Vinty's mummy<br><br><i>\"Omg, you're out with EXCELIA!?\"</i> - Vinty's sister<br><br><i>\"Fantastic story!\"</i> - RealReviewer23",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676130/extras/b16c602969b613c62dbe6d88d7255257.avif?t=1737936895\" width=660 height=198 /></span><br><br>Singaporeans have reported ghost sightings of Kiki, a calligrapher who had passed away several years ago. Meanwhile, Vinty receives a mysterious mail with a plane ticket to Singapore. As an aspiring calligrapher, she must learn the truth behind those Kiki appearances.<br><br>Even in death, Kiki continues to steal the spotlight. Must Vinty remain as a nobody for as long as she lives (yeah, probably)?<br><br><i>\"Make sure you stay hydrated honey!\" </i>- Vinty's mummy<br><br><i>\"Omg, you're out with EXCELIA!?\"</i> - Vinty's sister<br><br><i>\"Fantastic story!\"</i> - RealReviewer23",
